 /> <br />\n<br />\n今日佢要結婚喇  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從此揾到一個將你視如珍寶既男人 <br />\n今生今世佢唔會再比你流一滴眼淚<br />\n好鄧佢開心 而我都得到我應有既懲罰 失去一生最愛 永遠翻唔到轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係咁 但冇辦法"},{"pid":"368bd794efcd29134dbb3337e044af0e8f1e5048","tid":833291,"uid":48294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"let her go"},{"pid":"84d0fef3c7d6f02a15b4752cacf286a8277daaca","tid":833291,"uid":188150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:03:01.000Z","msg":"頂得順你4年，你個ex有一顆好強大既心。"}]}